column4: As a customer I should be able to login
column5:
Login page should have below details:

-Username and Password:
User ID:User ID: <textbox min 5 and max 20>
Password: A text value for Password(Maximum 30 characters, Minimum one upper case, lower case and special character )

-Error message:
Displaying appropriate specific error message for invalid input..

-Successful Login:
User should redirected to a dashboard/Home page with role specifc options in it.

column4: As a Customer, I want to be able to self register into the system with my details.
column5:
Consumer should be able to enter the following information in the screen;
1.Personal Information:
- Customer Name: A text value for Customer name(Maximum 50 characters)
- Email: A text field to capture the Email.
- Mobile number: <select box and text box)
- After choosing the country code, 10 digit mobile number should be entered in text box
-Address: A text value for complete mailing Address, including ZIP code and Postal code

2.Username and Password:
- User ID: <textbox min 5 and max 20>
- Password: A text value for Password(Maximum 30 characters)
- Confirm Password: A text value for confirm password(Maximum 30 characters)

3.Preferences:
-Specify any preferences related to mail delivery, notifications, or other relevant options

- Register: Submit button.
- Reset : Reset button

* After clicking the 'Register' button, a registration acknowledgment screen need to be displayed with a success message. "Consumer  Registration successful." in green color. 
* Also display the following attributes in the Acknowledgment screen; Customer username(Randomly generated), Customer Name and Email.

column4: As a Customer, I want to view the Home Page with features.
column5:
* After login to the system using the customerId and password, customer can view the home page with following information in the screen;
- At the right side, display Welcome <username>, 
- Top bar, have following menu
   1)Home - onclicking it redirect to the same page .
   2)Booking service- On clicking it should be able to proceed with the booking.
   3)Tracking - On clicking it should be navigated to Tracking Screen
   4)Previous Booking – On clicking it Should be navigated to Previous Booking Screen.                        
  5) Contact Support- On clicking it  Should be redirected to support page/ helper page                     
  6) Logout – on clicking it should redirect to login page of the project, by clearing the userdetails from browser

column4: As a Customer, I should to be able to book the service from Postal Management System
column5:
Below details needs to be displayed :
1. Sender Information: (This need to pre-populate as read only  based on the current user)
-Name
-Address
-Contact details
2. Receiver Information/Customer information:
-Name
-Address
-Pin Code
-Contact details
3. Parcel Details:
-Size and weight
-Contents description (for tracking and safety)
4. Shipping Options:
-Choose delivery speed (standard, express, etc.)
-Select packaging preferences (Standard Packaging, Custom Packaging, Eco-friendly Packaging, Fragile Item handling)
5. Date and Time Selection:
-Choose preferred pickup or drop-off time
6. Service Cost and Payment:
-Display the cost based on the chosen options (Parcel Size, Shipping options)
-Provide different payment methods
7.Additional Services:
-Insurance options
-Tracking services
8. Implement all possible validations with custom validation messages.

column4: As a Customer, I want to be able to  pay the booking service bill from "Booking Service Page"
column5:
In the Payment page, customer can view the following information in the screen;
- At the right side  , Welcome <username>, Logout button<onclicking it should be logged out>  
- Payment page should display the below details
 a) Bill Amount (should not be editable by the customer)
 b) Mode of Payment – Debit/Credit
    - Pay Now button - On Clicking will proceed to screen for entering the card details
    - Back to Home - On Clicking , it should redirect to booking service page
On clicking the Pay Now button, it should be redirected to Screen where   Customer can provide his Credit Card details to pay the bill
   -Credit Card <text as title>:(Read only)
   -Card No  <16 digits>
   -Card Holder Name 
   -Expiry Date <MM/YY>
   -CVV < 3 digits>
- Make Payment<button >
- On clicking the Make Payment button, "Payment Successful" message along with  Booking ID and redirect to invoice page
- Use javascript for the necessary actions.

column4: As a customer/officer once the payment is successful an invoice page need to be displayed
column5:
The invoice page need to contain the below detail read only with print option
-Receiver Name
-Receiver Address
-Receiver Pin
-Receiver Mobile
-Parcel Weight(g)
-Parcel Contents Description
-Parcel Delivery Type
-Parcel Packing Preference
-Parcel Pickup Time
-Parcel Dropoff Time
-Parcel Service Cost
-Parcel Payment Time

column4: As a Customer, I want to be able to track the status of my parcel by providing the tracking numbers.
column5:
* Customer can able to enter the following information in the screen;
After successful shipping of the package customer should be able to view the tracking status of the package which he/she boooked by providing the following details.:
- Booking ID- A 12 digit number that is randomly generated after booking a package(Unique code)
- Search button- Once clicked the page should display the status of the package.

column4: As a Officer, I want to be able to check the status of a customer's package.
column5:
* After login to the system using the userId and password of the Officer , he/she can view the  page with following information in the screen;
- List of all the shipped package sorted latest on the top
- A search box where the Officer can provide the Customer ID and Booking Id of a particular Customer.
- Search button
- Once clicked the page should display the status of the package.

column4: As an Officer I want to be able to schedule pick-up of packages from the sender.
column5:
* The following details should be displayed for the officer to schedule a pickup:
Officer should have option to search with Booking ID based on the result officer should able to provide a date and time after consultation with Customer
- Booking ID of a particular customer
- Date and Time
 
a save button should save the information to the system. with proper message and validation.

column4: As an officer I want to update the delivery status of the particular item
